
|WKBSyntax
=================|YKB

newbie <msg>
enewbie <msg>|YKO

Where <msg>  is the string you want to say.

The newbie channel is solely for new-player questions and answers. Players
from level 6 through 20 are marked (Newer), while more experienced players
are marked (Helper). Non-newbies with general conversation should use other,
more appropriate channels.

|CKBNOTE: Newbies are players level 5 and under.
